.TH "LIGHTNING-PEER_LATENCY" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-peer-latency \- show connection status for a peer
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning peer-latency
.I peer_id
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns the connection status for a peer. Ping time is not directly available and is reported as N/A.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
